node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People Brough @entrepreneursquote (A (Athr) hread)'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Always wanted to read The 7 Habits Of Highly Effective People? Get the main takeaways in just 3 minutes with this overview.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1) Sharpen the saw Don't work yourself to death. Strive for sustainable lifestyle that affords you time to recuperate, recharge and be effective in the long-term.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2) Be proactive. You have a natural need to wield influence on the world arouno you sO don't spend your time just reacting to external events and circumstances. Take charge and assume responsibility for your life.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3) Begin with an end in mind. Don't spend your life working aimlessly, tackling whatever job is at hand. Have a vision for the future and align your actions accordingly to make it into a reality.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4) Put first things first. To prioritize your work, focus on what's important, meaning the things that bring you closer to your vision of the future. uture Don't get distracted by urgent but unimportant tasks.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5) Think win-win. When negotiating with others, don't try to get the biggest slice of the cake, but rather find a division that is acceptable to all parties. You will still get your fai share and build strong positive relationships in the process.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Seek first to understand then to be understood. When someone presents US with a problem, we often jump right to giving a solution. This is a mistake. We should first take time to really listen to the other person and only then make recommendations.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7) Synergize. Adopt the guiding principle that in a group, the contributions of many will far exceed those of any individual. This will will help you achieve goals you could never have reached on your own.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Lessons from the book HABITS OF HIGHLY EFFECTIVE PEOPLE Stephen R. Covey RosettaBooks® Drop a in the comments if you learned something!'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 16, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'If you don't separate yourself from your distractions, your distractions will separate you from your goals and the life you want.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1) Learn something new every day. 2) Things can and do change very quickly. Be ready. 3) Enjoy time spent with your family.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4) Get a clear plan in place for your mental health. 5) Don't be too hard on yourself. Learn and move on. 6) Be honest with yourself.'.
Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7) Get your morning routine sorted. 8) Start writing things down. Travel as often and as far as you can.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '10) Give without expecting to receive anything in return. 11) Find what you are grateful for. 12) Don't waste time with jerks.'.
Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '13) Take responsibility for everything. 14) Take action beyond your comfort zone. 15) Be patient.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '16) Enjoy the small moments along the way. 17) Speak up, or others will speak up for you. 18) Don't be afraid to begin something new.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Days are passing by incredibly rapidly, and it's so easy to waste ots of timer time. I've not mastered it yet, but am giving my best to eliminate time-wasters.'.
Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'And... Now it's your turn. What is #1 thing you've learned the haro way?'.
